      • configure

        public void configure(InRange range)
        Tells this generator to produce values within a specified minimum and/or maximum, inclusive, with uniform distribution. InRange.min() and InRange.max() take precedence over InRange.minByte() and InRange.maxByte(), if non-empty.
        Parameters:
        range - annotation that gives the range's constraints
